videos.description: Tyler Nelson uses a nice shot fake, allowing him to drain a 3-pointer for Fairfield.
videos.headline: Nelson's good ball fake leads to 3-pointer

videos.description: Rickey McGill finds a cutting Roland Griffin who scores for Iona.
videos.headline: McGill good pass leads to Griffin layup

videos.description: Zach Lewis makes an acrobatic layup for Iona just as the first half ends.
videos.headline: Lewis goes coast-to-coast to score right before half

videos.description: Roland Griffin makes a tough layup then hustles down court to make a big chase-down block for Iona.
videos.headline: Griffin scores and picks up a big block on the other end

videos.description: Zach Lewis tosses up a lob up to TK Edogi who rises up and throws down the dunk with one hand for Iona.
videos.headline: Edogi dunks down alley-oop with one hand

videos.description: Tyler Nelson makes a good adjustment while in the air and still buries a 3-pointer for Fairfield.
videos.headline: Nelson hangs in the air as long as he can and hits 3

videos.description: After defeating Fairfield in the MAAC championship  Iona clinches a spot in the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Iona punches its ticket to the big dance

videos.description: The Gaels are dancing after defeating Fairfield 83-71, earning Iona a MAAC 3-peat.
videos.headline: Iona punches ticket to NCAA Tournament
